title: S8E14 – "Visceral Visions " – Scary Stories Told in the Dark
description:
In this episode of Scary Stories Told in the Dark, we bring you three spine-chilling tales from author J.C. Barnard, performed by host and narrator Otis Jiry, about devilish documentaries, lunatic labyrinths, and evil experiments.
